#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/introduction.rst:19
msgid ""
"The Radius allows you to directly control the width of the extrusion "
"along the \"spinal\" curve. The *Radius* of the points is set using the "
"*Shrink/Fatten Radius* transform tool :kbd:`Alt-S`, the "
":menuselection:`Curve --> Transform --> Shrink/Fatten Radius`, or the "
":menuselection:`Properties region --> Transform --> Radius`."
msgstr ""
"Le rayon (Radius) vous permet de contrôler directement la largeur de "
"l'extrusion le long de la courbe \"spinale\". Le rayon des points est "
"défini en utilisant l'outil de transformation *Shrink/Fatten Radius* "
":kbd:`Alt-S`, :menuselection:`Curve --> Transform --> Shrink/Fatten "
"Radius`, ou :menuselection:`Properties region --> Transform --> Radius`."

